Grant Mitchell (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Grant_Mitchell_(actor) 0 John Grant Mitchell Jr. (June 17, 1874 – May 1, 1957) was an American stage actor on Broadway and mainly a character actor on film. He appeared on Broadway from 1902 to 1939 and appeared in more than 125 films between 1930 and 1948.
